  <brief_title>Evaluation of Hemodynamics and Amount of Blood Flowing Through the Kidneys by Measuring Some Physiological Substances in Blood and Urines</brief_title>
  <official_title>Hemodynamic Indexes and Renal Perfusion: Indirect Evaluation of Blood Volume Using the Association Between ScvO2 and Urinary Electrolytes in Patients Undergoing Major Surgery.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
