  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to verify any existing relationship between mixed oxygen
      saturation (from central venous catheter) and urinary sodium, potassium, chloride in
      determining the volemic state and renal perfusion of patients undergoing major surgical
      interventions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
