  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Determination of mixed oxygen saturation in central venous blood (ScvO2) and three urinary electrolytes (sodium, potassium, chloride)</measure>
    <time_frame>During the stay of the patient in the operating room (in average 6 hours) and the eventual stay in the post-surgery intensive care unit (in average 1 day)</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
